name: Mommy, I was Born to Ride Romper
description:
This adorable romper is perfect for your little rider.  A vintage shirt was used for it's fabulous fabric to create this  one of a kind romper for your special boy. Once it is gone, it is gone.   This outfit features a hidden zipper, so you don't need to worry about buttons, and a velcro closing at the crotch. 

Fabric is pre shrunk 100% cotton

Size: 18 months. 
Rompers are available in Sizes: Newborn to 18 Months

Shipping included

name: Flower Scarf
description:
These hand made scarfs are the perfect accessory for any season. The flower is the  center piece of this scarf with wispy tendrils of chain stitching hanging down for a great, fresh new look. This scarf can be made for adults and children.  The length of the chain tendrils are , Adult 42" long and the child's scarf measures 27" to 32". This scarf is available in any color yarn or multicolored yarn.
